data.description: Resort Living at Its Best!...This Bear Paw Resort home features a panorama wall of windows looking out on Lake Hiwassee.  Savor your vistas from two decks that soar into the trees; indoors, the open floor plan is bathed with natural light. Lovely kitchen with breakfast bar, windowed dining space. Adjacent living room has inviting stone fireplace, vaulted beamed ceiling. You'll love the main level master suite with private bath; bonus guest bed and bath, plus lower level family room and additional bathroom. Attention to detail shows in gleaming wood floors, terraced garden beds, and nice landscaping. Gated community with pool, tennis, clubhouse, and marina. Move-in ready to enjoy now!
